quran[9{c,v,t}:
10,62,"sunooooooo! jo Allah ke dost hain, jo imaan laaye aur jinhon ne taqwa ka rawayya ikhtiyar kya ,"
10,63,un ke liye kisi khauf aur ranj ka mauqa nahi hai
10,64,duniya aur akhirat dono zindagion mein un ke liye basharat hi basharat hai Allah ki baatein badal nahi sakteen yahi barri kamyabi hai
10,65,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jo baatein yeh log tujh par banatay hain woh tujhe ranjida nah karen, azzt saari ki saari khuda ke ikhtiyar mein hai, aur woh sab kuch santa aur jaanta hai"
10,66,"aagah raho! aasman ke basnay walay hon ya zameen ke, sab se sab Allah ke mamlook hain aur jo log Allah ke siwa kuch ( apne khodsakht_h ) sharikon ko pukaar rahay hain woh niray wahm- o- gumaan ke pairo hain aur mehez qiyaas aarayyan karte hain"
10,67,woh Allah hi hai jis ne tumahray liye raat banai ke is mein sukoon haasil karo aur din ko roshan banaya is mein nishanain hain unn logon ke liye jo ( khulay kaanon se paighambar ki dawat ko ) suntay hain
10,68,"logon ne keh diya ke Allah ne kisi ko beta banaya hai subhan Allah ! woh to be niaz hai, asmano aur zameen mein jo kuch hai sab is ki malik hai tumahray paas is qoul ke liye aakhir kya Daleel hai? kya tum Allah ke mutaliq woh baatein kehte ho jo tumahray ilm mein nahi hain ?"
10,69,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, keh do ke jo log Allah par jhutay aftara bandhte hain woh hargiz Falah nahi pa satke"
10,70,"duniya ki chand roza zindagi mein mazay kar len, phir hamari taraf unn ko palatna hai phir hum is kufar ke badlay jis ka irtikaab woh kar rahay hain un ko sakht azaab ka maza chkhayin ge"
